  "extras": {
    "summary": "A CONCURRENT RESOLUTION PROPOSING AN AMENDMENT TO SECTION 253, MISSISSIPPI CONSTITUTION OF 1890, TO CREATE A STATE SUFFRAGE RESTORATION PANEL TO PROVIDE AN ALTERNATE METHOD FOR THE RIGHT TO VOTE TO BE RESTORED TO ELIGIBLE PERSONS CONVICTED OF A NONVIOLENT DISENFRANCHISING CRIME, AND TO SECTION 241, MISSISSIPPI CONSTITUTION OF 1890, TO INCLUDE HUMAN TRAFFICKING, ATTEMPTED MURDER AND SEXUAL BATTERY IN THE LIST OF DISENFRANCHISING CRIMES; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
